  <h3> What you’ll need for your DIY flower vase:</h3>
    <h4>Glass bottle, any size</h4>
    <h4>Yarn </h4>
    <h4>Pure acetone </h4>
    <h4>Lighter </h4>
    <h4>Pitcher of cold water</h4>
    <h4>Sandpaper </h4>
    <h4>Painter’s tape </h4>
    <h4>Acrylic paint, any color </h4>
